{"tid":635257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改中史課本字眼　楊潤雄：中國一直有港主權　「收回」不正確「位於中國南方」不清晰","createTime":"2018-04-20T03:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9720f13794f23be733598b081b60cdcd4a1114ff","tid":635257,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"有線新聞早前教育局今年審核歷史課本時，要求出版局修改「香港位於中國南方」、「中國收回香港」等一直沿用的字眼。教育局局長楊潤雄在立法會財務委員會特別會議上回應議員提問時指，中國一直擁有香港主權，故「收回」之說並不正確。郭家麟反譏當局，不如使用中共黨史或內地教科書，楊潤雄回應時指稱可考慮使用國家的教科書，他又指不反對香港教科書出版社用內地教科書作參考。<br />\n<br />\n議員郭家麒質問楊潤雄這一年來發生過甚麼事，為何當局一直容許使用有關字句，但今年卻需要修改。楊潤雄指，審核教科書時必須要顧及前文後理。楊潤雄舉例指，「香港位於中國的南方」在語文上不清晰，可以代表香港在中國境內或境外的南方，故有需要修改。<br />\n<br />\n對於「中國收回香港」一說，楊潤雄指，歷史上中國一直具有香港的主權，所以不涉及任何收回，或由英國交回香港主權的說法。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麟譏用內地教科書   楊潤雄：會考慮下<br />\n<br />\n郭家麟在提問時，以反詰口脗說，既然要書商猜度政治正確的思想，「不如將中共黨史或內地教科書俾我哋」。楊潤雄回應時指：「郭家麒議員提議話將國家的教科書擺嚟香港，如果係郭家麒提議，我會考慮下。」楊潤雄又指，不反對香港教科書出版社用內地教科書作參考，「因為佢哋可以攞各類的書嚟參考」。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞早前取得一份教育局的課本評審報告，發現今年中史課本內的不少字眼都被要求修改，包括「香港主權移交中國內地」、「中共一黨專政」等以往一直沿用的說法。浸會大學新聞系高級講師呂秉權質疑，有關做法是否出於政治需要，又形容「黑手」正伸向和滲透香港歷史教科書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/改中史書字眼-楊潤雄-中國一直有香港主權-收回-之說不正確-香港位於中國南方-不清晰/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%9B%B8%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A-%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E-%E4%B9%8B%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%8D%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%2F&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=d9d12e15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%B2%E6%9B%B8%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A-%E6%94%B6%E5%9B%9E-%E4%B9%8B%E8%AA%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%8D%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9-%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0%2F&h=9e97a9a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/改中史書字眼-楊潤雄-中國一直有香港主權-收回-之說不正確-香港位於中國南方-不清晰/</a>"},{"pid":"400cef3367d43bdaa706dab7908578bbd2b39e37","tid":635257,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"97前香港唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca5a09748ac1755d190ade18ff34678d5605f9e","tid":635257,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"一直？點一直法？<br />\n有地球開始？"},{"pid":"127c515f2fd26940499159b85cdc42646ce549f4","tid":635257,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ca5a09748ac1755d190ade18ff34678d5605f9e","tid":635257,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"一直？點一直法？<br />\n有地球開始？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"黨說一直有，就一直有"},{"pid":"4de3f84abaabda0f806dd3fce4945ef057583a20","tid":635257,"uid":36901,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://history.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0829/c372327-25564733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhistory.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn%2F2014%2F0829%2Fc372327-25564733.html&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=482db26c\" target=\"_blank\">http://history.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0829/c372327-25564733.html</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧小平說，香港的主權是中國的。中國要維護香港作為自由港和國際金融中心的地位，也不影響外國人在那裡的投資。在這個前提下，由香港人，包括在香港的外國人管理香港。他說，香港有了地方政府，我們的新憲法有規定，允許建立特別行政區，由香港人自己組成政府，不管是華人、英國人或其他人都可參加，可作政府雇員嘛，甚至成為香港政府的成員都可考慮，各種制度也不變&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鄧小平坦率地對希思說，我們是多年的好朋友了，如果中國到那時不把香港主權收回來，我們這些人誰也交不了帳。</span><br />\n<br />\n希思連連點頭說，條約裡也寫得清楚。<br />\n<br />\n狗膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然話人民日報,鄧小平都措辭不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81fb62b199bc7f825466c225a1cafc4d04e4455","tid":635257,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"一直有主權？<br />\n咁點解香港、九龍叫「割讓」，新界叫「租借」，要咁區分？"},{"pid":"7a01ce663307bbaef6a2ab31ef0fd407faa67c04","tid":635257,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4de3f84abaabda0f806dd3fce4945ef057583a20","tid":635257,"uid":36901,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://history.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0829/c372327-25564733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhistory.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn%2F2014%2F0829%2Fc372327-25564733.html&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=482db26c\" target=\"_blank\">http://history.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0829/c372327-25564733.html</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧小平說，香港的主權是中國的。中國要維護香港作為自由港和國際金融中心的地位，也不影響外國人在那裡的投資。在這個前提下，由香港人，包括在香港的外國人管理香港。他說，香港有了地方政府，我們的新憲法有規定，允許建立特別行政區，由香港人自己組成政府，不管是華人、英國人或其他人都可參加，可作政府雇員嘛，甚至成為香港政府的成員都可考慮，各種制度也不變&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鄧小平坦率地對希思說，我們是多年的好朋友了，如果中國到那時不把香港主權收回來，我們這些人誰也交不了帳。</span><br />\n<br />\n希思連連點頭說，條約裡也寫得清楚。<br />\n<br />\n狗膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然話人民日報,鄧小平都措辭不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:01:09.000Z","msg":"局長：鄧小平識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a5db5c33cf476d236ea78df3d3152ee9e0d987","tid":635257,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c81fb62b199bc7f825466c225a1cafc4d04e4455","tid":635257,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"一直有主權？<br />\n咁點解香港、九龍叫「割讓」，新界叫「租借」，要咁區分？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"反了<br />\n佢想話清朝唔係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595f5b457ab779e2a62bba3ec63a6a40c0e06a59","tid":635257,"uid":115467,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"拎返份租借割讓合約出黎睇吓先囉～呀！份 合約係台灣喎～～～"},{"pid":"b119ff83e882beda32e221816faaeb4f01560779","tid":635257,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:07:55.000Z","msg":"唔通係東邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbc566a6ec80f5891849ac623898a841da9421f","tid":635257,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"The Declaration entered into force with the exchange of instruments of ratification on 27 May 1985, and was registered by the PRC and UK governments at the United Nations on 12 June 1985. In the Joint Declaration, the PRC Government stated that it had decided <span style=\"color: red;\">to resume the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong</span> (including Hong Kong Island, Kowloon, and the New Territories) with effect from 1 July 1997, and the UK Government declared that it would hand over Hong Kong to the PRC with effect from 1 July 1997. The PRC Government also declared its basic policies regarding Hong Kong in the document.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sino-British_Joint_Declaration\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSino-British_Joint_Declaration&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=1e39fcef\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sino-British_Joint_Declaration</a><br />\n<br />\n吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n局方說法係「對香港恢復行使主權」，即係主權一直有，不過冇「行使」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e3e5928de76638f68ce7aa850b7f3d7a7a2005","tid":635257,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a04f9c4afb957961cc125b1b6cc0b02f8d864c6","tid":635257,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"我會即時問下局長符拉迪沃斯托克主權係咪係小支那度? <br />\n同俄佬係1860年清朝與俄羅斯帝國簽訂清俄北京條約有冇效<br />\n<br />\n點解1842, 1862, 1898年果3條唔係條約，同北極熊果條就咁尊重呢? <br />\n<br />\nfrom wiki<br />\n<br />\n在1858年，清黑龍江將軍奕山在俄羅斯帝國的壓力下簽訂《璦琿條約》，規定包括海參崴的烏蘇里江以東地區為清俄共管。兩年後的1860年，第二次鴉片戰爭結束後，俄國又與清政府簽訂《清俄北京條約》[11]，清政府割讓了烏蘇里江以東包括庫頁島在內的約40萬平方千米的領土，其中包括海參崴&mdash;俄國未來在遠東發展政策上最重要的港口。"},{"pid":"b88d3ee6f462c2feccd003537c80c4d5794af29f","tid":635257,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中華民國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6ce5d079a6d2a0fa0c3728cb2d6d0fdd948368","tid":635257,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"過多十年，史書就係改到<br />\n<br />\n1997年，香港廣大市民懷著熱愛祖囯的心實現統一，令香港土地從英狗手中獻回祖囯大家庭"},{"pid":"13c009cee10dfd7735dec0f24c76908ac08222dd","tid":635257,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd6ce5d079a6d2a0fa0c3728cb2d6d0fdd948368","tid":635257,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:19:58.000Z","msg":"過多十年，史書就係改到<br />\n<br />\n1997年，香港廣大市民懷著熱愛祖囯的心實現統一，令香港土地從英狗手中獻回祖囯大家庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"其實已經做緊呢類文宣洗下一代腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03298119d5b513e49625b0d5704ded01bc1256fe","tid":635257,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/preamble.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fpreamble.html&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=32b08cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/preamble.html</a><br />\n<br />\n序言<br />\n<br />\n香港自古以來就是中國的領土，一八四○年鴉片戰爭以後被英國佔領。一九八四年十二月十九日，中英兩國政府簽署了關於香港問題的聯合聲明，確認中華人民共和國政府於一九九七年七月一日恢復對香港行使主權，<strong>從而實現了長期以來中國人民收回香港的共同願望</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n改埋基本法啊唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc0c71c6f8581c8dcb6f8824d2201d53516a7d4","tid":635257,"uid":776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32a223ae5b7692f9463aaf80d612c3a75547a3f8","tid":635257,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:27:15.000Z","msg":"依單野超離譜wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 有沒方法搞搞他"},{"pid":"10108ef2ecafa674a64f0d893e971a3f3c8ab952","tid":635257,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dbc566a6ec80f5891849ac623898a841da9421f","tid":635257,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:10:27.000Z","msg":"The Declaration entered into force with the exchange of instruments of ratification on 27 May 1985, and was registered by the PRC and UK governments at the United Nations on 12 June 1985. In the Joint Declaration, the PRC Government stated that it had decided <span style=\"color: red;\">to resume the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong</span> (including Hong Kong Island, Kowloon, and the New Territories) with effect from 1 July 1997, and the UK Government declared that it would hand over Hong Kong to the PRC with effect from 1 July 1997. The PRC Government also declared its basic policies regarding Hong Kong in the document.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sino-British_Joint_Declaration\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSino-British_Joint_Declaration&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=1e39fcef\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sino-British_Joint_Declaration</a><br />\n<br />\n吹佢唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n局方說法係「對香港恢復行使主權」，即係主權一直有，不過冇「行使」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:40:13.000Z","msg":"中英聯合聲明第一條嘅中方聲明就係咁寫<br />\n呢句冇英方份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7f9fa81462ba1ccd9066ee06fa88e09baf64e9","tid":635257,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"連承認真實歷史勇氣都冇呢d國家點會有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e163f113b912149538585bf070fc461360228639","tid":635257,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb7f9fa81462ba1ccd9066ee06fa88e09baf64e9","tid":635257,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"連承認真實歷史勇氣都冇呢d國家點會有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:35:04.000Z","msg":"連個國都係偷番嚟<br />\n你叫人地點面對呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63e0c917688b92a9dbf91b5b8ce66cf9c98ad90","tid":635257,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"條撚樣個腦是智障！"}]}